 Zero-Day ML Engine:
   * Random Forest + SVM + Naive Bayes + RuleBased classifier ensemble
   * Welford online baseline profiling for anomaly detection
   * Standalone zeroday mode with crawl → ML → fuzz → HPP → exploit pipeline
   * Training mode for custom model fitting
 .
 Features:
   * AI-powered zero-day detection with multi-classifier ensemble
   * ML-based anomaly scoring with statistical baselines
    * Concurrent fuzzing with BlazingShadow™ architecture (3 workers)
    * COMMUNITY color palette with Kali Linux gradient theme (by Lyara-Koroleva)
